Round 1

[Patient] Can you recommend heart-healthy foods for me?
[Educator] Sure! Include more fruits, veggies, whole grains, and lean proteins in your diet.

Round 2

[Patient] Are there specific foods I should avoid?
[Educator] Limit salt, sugar, and saturated fats. Avoid processed foods and sugary drinks.

Round 3

[Patient] What about drinks? Any recommendations?
[Educator] Stay hydrated with water. Limit alcohol and sugary drinks. Herbal teas can be a good choice.

Round 4

[Patient] I love soul food. Can I still enjoy it?
[Educator] Yes! Try lighter versions with less salt and fat. Use herbs and spices for flavor.

Round 5

[Patient] Any other tips for maintaining a healthy diet?
[Educator] Eat smaller, more frequent meals. Practice portion control. Listen to your body's hunger cues.